<s> We were talking only within your first point.  </s>
<s> Assuming that we need a diff format, we are arguing that we are better off with a text-based format thna an optimal but opaque binary format (with its problems of non-debuggability, byte-ordering, etc.).  </s>
<s> In an authoring context, we must also consider that diffs are not always the output of some automatic process...  </s>
